{"folder":"pa1iFJDN5vnbh7cz","name":"Art (Photography)","type":"skill","img":"systems/brp/assets/Icons/skills.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Use this skill to create a work of art in paint or sculpture, or to compose a story, poem, or musical work. A critical or special success yields a timeless classic of considerably more value and prestige, a failure is mediocre hackwork, and a fumble may harm the creator&rsquo;s reputation.</p>\n<p>You would use Perform for acting, dancing, singing, or&nbsp;playing a musical&nbsp; instrument.</p>\n<p><strong>Specialties</strong>: Calligraphy, Composing, Conceptual Art, Digital Art, Drawing, Painting, Photography, Poetry, Sculpture, Sketching, Songwriting, Writing, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>Setting Notes</strong>: Art is universal, though it may have era- or settingspecific specialties.</p>","gmDescription":"","subType":"","base":5,"xp":0,"profession":0,"personality":0,"personal":0,"effects":0,"baseFormula":{"1":{"stat":"fixed","value":0},"2":{"stat":"fixed","value":0},"Func":"or"},"noXP":false,"category":"mnplmod","chosen":true,"specialism":true,"group":false,"groupSkills":[],"prsnlty":false,"variable":false,"specName":"Photography","mainName":"Art","occupation":false,"improve":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"brp","systemVersion":"11.0.37","coreVersion":"11.315","createdTime":1699084864720,"modifiedTime":1702582643340,"lastModifiedBy":"NiJh555W408VQRFB"},"_id":"EXCdnUOhJ9OdZQCz","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"NiJh555W408VQRFB":3}}
{"folder":"TObATz4QmCl9DsS4","name":"Pilot (Starship)","type":"skill","img":"systems/brp/assets/Icons/skills.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Use this skill to steer, maneuver, and control a vehicle through the air, on or under the water, or in space. Larger vehicles may require multiple pilots, and a roll should be made every four hours when not in combat, and once per round during combat or when performing vehicular maneuvers.</p>\n<p><strong>Specialties:</strong> Airplane, Airship, Balloon, Boat, Helicopter, Hovercraft, Jet Aircraft, Jetpack, Starship, Submarine, etc. At the gamemaster&rsquo;s discretion, a pilot may pilot a vessel with a similar specialty as if Difficult. If successful, make an&nbsp; experience check. If the experience roll is successful, start a new skill with a specialty at that rating, plus the gained experience.</p>\n<p><strong>Effects</strong>: Most day-to-day piloting is Automatic&mdash;roll only under adverse conditions or for extraordinary situations. A fumble almost inevitably causes an engine to stall or even crash, failing means the destination is not reached in the desired timeframe, success gets where one desires, and superior successes yield more expert piloting and results. See Aerial Combat and Chases rules for more information, and the Chase Trouble table&nbsp;for mishaps.</p>","gmDescription":"","subType":"","base":1,"xp":0,"profession":0,"personality":0,"personal":0,"effects":0,"baseFormula":{"1":{"stat":"fixed","value":0},"2":{"stat":"fixed","value":0},"Func":"or"},"noXP":false,"category":"physmod","chosen":true,"specialism":true,"group":false,"groupSkills":[],"prsnlty":false,"variable":false,"specName":"Starship","mainName":"Pilot","occupation":false,"improve":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{}},"_stats":{"systemId":"brp","systemVersion":"11.0.37","coreVersion":"11.315","createdTime":1699092618107,"modifiedTime":1702582643340,"lastModifiedBy":"NiJh555W408VQRFB"},"_id":"F1aVcUEZCSDI0Lyc","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"NiJh555W408VQRFB":3}}
